# API-Experiment

This is an API project using NodeJS, ExpressJS, and MongoDB. The goal of this project is to try testing API Auth endpoints using Jest and Supertest.

# Features

- Register new users
- Login user and return access token
- Fetch user's profile data
- Update user's profile data
- Delete user's profile data
- Logout users

# Getting Started

## Installation

Clone the repository

    npm install

## Usage

Start for development

    npm run dev

Start for production

    npm run start

Run tests

    npm run testB01
    npm run testB02
    npm run testB03
    npm run testB04
    npm run testB05
    npm run testBA


    B is the project name, and the number is the test number.
    The BA test is to test all the suits in the project.

The project can be tested using Postman to check the endpoints.

The endpoints are:

- POST /api/v1/auth/register
- POST /api/v1/auth/login
- GET /api/v1/auth/profile
- PUT /api/v1/auth/profile
- DELETE /api/v1/auth/profile
- GET /api/v1/auth/logout
